WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.000
On a quiet winter morning, a little bird was lost. A child noticed the bird and felt curious.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
The little bird felt scared.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Grandma gently reminded the child to be careful. Little animals need kindness and space.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:32.000
The child learned to stay calm and quiet together.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:40.000
They helped the bird find its way home.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:52.000
The little bird was safe again; helping made the child feel proud and happy.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Protecting animals shows care for all life.
